flowchart LR
  A[Candidate models] --> B[Eval corpus]
  B --> C[Golden queries]
  C --> D[Metrics comparison]
  D --> E[Chosen model]
  E --> F[Embed corpus]
  F --> G[(New vector index)]
  H[User query] --> I[Same model]
  I --> J[Query vector]
  G --> K[Dense or hybrid retrieval]
  J --> K
  K --> L[Eval gate + shadow test]
  L --> M[Release or rollback]
